@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam rectangleBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #1565C0

title 接口契约与候选图提交流程（当前实现对齐版）

rectangle "Optimizer生成\nmutation proposal" as Gen
rectangle "XML/XSD\n结构校验" as XSD
rectangle "语义图校验\n(validate_graph)" as Static
rectangle "L1 Sandbox Gate\n(抽象门控)" as Sandbox
rectangle "L2 A/B Shadow\n(比较器)" as AB
rectangle "Policy Reviewer\n+ Hooks" as Policy
rectangle "ConnectionEngine\ncommit graph" as Hotload
rectangle "AutoRollback\npost-commit probes" as Rollback

Gen --> XSD
XSD --> Static : 通过
XSD --> Gen : 失败(反馈错误)

Static --> Sandbox : 通过
Static --> Gen : 失败(反馈错误)

Sandbox --> AB : 通过
Sandbox --> Gen : 失败(反馈错误)

AB --> Policy : 通过
AB --> Gen : 失败(反馈错误)

Policy --> Hotload : 批准
Policy --> Gen : 否决(强惩罚)

Hotload --> Rollback : 上线后退化
Hotload --> "新配置生效" : 稳定运行

note right of Static
  当前实现包含：
  - duplicate connection
  - unknown component / port
  - payload mismatch
  - required input completeness
  - protected slot override
  - cycle detection
  - orphan detection
end note

@enduml
